# Database Entity Design

Migration workflow → see `prisma.mdc`.

## Naming
| Layer | Convention | Example |
|-------|------------|---------|
| Prisma model | PascalCase | `MenuItem` |
| Prisma field | camelCase + `@map` | `nameEn` → `name_en` |
| Table | snake_case plural | `@@map("menu_items")` |
| Enum | PascalCase | `UserRole` |

## Required on business tables
`id` (UUID), `createdAt`, `updatedAt`; use `isActive` for soft-disable.

## Bilingual columns
Pair fields: `nameEn`/`nameAr`, `descriptionEn`/`descriptionAr`.

## Relations
Explicit `onDelete`; `@@index` on FKs and filters (`venueId`, `status`).

## Phase 0 models
`Venue`, `User`, `Terminal` — history in `docs/TEAM_LOG.md`
